  <Method>
    <Step type="STEP" image="Gringo%20Art's%20Salsa_20250816_100857.jpg">Peel tomatoes by blistering skins over stove burner.</Step>
    <Step type="STEP" image="">Chop tomatoes and add to food processor.</Step>
    <Step type="STEP" image="Gringo%20Art's%20Salsa_20250816_102131.jpg">Add onions, jalepeno, garlic, and seasonings to food processor.</Step>
    <Step type="STEP" image="Gringo%20Art's%20Salsa_20250816_101937.jpg">Add onions to skillet with a little EVOO, add dried chiles and brown the onions.</Step>
    <Step type="STEP" image="Gringo%20Art's%20Salsa_20250816_102248.jpg">Add onions and chiles and cilantro to food processor.</Step>
    <Step type="STEP" image="">Process to desired smoothness.</Step>
    <Step type="STEP" image="">Adjust seasoning, add a little molasses if needed depending on tartness of tomatoes.</Step>
    <Step type="STEP" image="">Chill for an hour before serving.</Step>
  </Method>
